About the Course
Heather Golf Club is a 9-hole golf course located in Weeki Wachee, FL, about 45 minutes north of Tampa in Hernando County, and near the famous mermaids of Weeki Wachee Springs. The course is a 2,354-yard, 9-hole layout, with beautiful live oaks and pines lining narrow and challenging fairways. Visit us today!
